{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Std/Internal/Do/Order/PreservesSup.html#Lean.Order.le_apply_of_point_meet_le\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Order</span>.<span class=\"name\">le_apply_of_point_meet_le</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">σ</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> v}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">β</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> w}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Internal/Order/Basic.html#Lean.Order.CompleteLattice\">CompleteLattice</a> <span class=\"fn\">β</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <span class=\"fn\">σ</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">pre</span> : <span class=\"fn\">β</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">Q</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">σ</span> → <span class=\"fn\">β</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">h</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Internal/Order/Basic.html#Lean.Order.PartialOrder.rel\">PartialOrder.rel</a> <span class=\"fn\">(fun (<span class=\"fn\">u</span> : <span class=\"fn\">σ</span>) =&gt; <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Std/Internal/Do/Order/Basic.html#Lean.Order.meet\">meet</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Std/Internal/Do/Order/Basic.html#Lean.Order.CompleteLattice.ofProp\">CompleteLattice.ofProp</a> (<span class=\"fn\">u</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\">s</span>))</span> <span class=\"fn\">pre</span></span>)</span> <span class=\"fn\">Q</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Internal/Order/Basic.html#Lean.Order.PartialOrder.rel\">PartialOrder.rel</a> <span class=\"fn\">pre</span> <span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">Q</span> <span class=\"fn\">s</span>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Frame a single state coordinate: from the function-order premise `(fun u => ⌜u = s⌝ ⊓ pre) ⊑ Q`\nconclude the point entailment `pre ⊑ Q s`. Instantiating the premise at `u := s` collapses\n`⌜s = s⌝ ⊓ pre` to `pre`. Iterating it over a state chain point-frames `pre ⊑ Q s₁ … sₙ` to the\nfunction-order goal `(fun u⃗ => ⌜u⃗ = s⃗⌝ ⊓ pre) ⊑ Q`. ","docLink":"./Std/Internal/Do/Order/PreservesSup.html#Lean.Order.le_apply_of_point_meet_le","kind":"theorem","line":137,"name":"Lean.Order.le_apply_of_point_meet_le","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Std/Internal/Do/Order/PreservesSup.lean#L137-L143"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Std/Internal/Do/Order/PreservesSup.html#Lean.Order.PreservesSup.frameClosure_le\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Order</span>.<span class=\"name\">PreservesSup</span>.<span class=\"name\">frameClosure_le</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Internal/Order/Basic.html#Lean.Order.CompleteLattice\">CompleteLattice</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">R</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> v}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">β</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> w}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">op</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">R</span> → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span> → <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\">∀ (<span class=\"fn\">r</span> : <span class=\"fn\">R</span>), <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Std/Internal/Do/Order/PreservesSup.html#Lean.Order.PreservesSup\">PreservesSup</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">op</span> <span class=\"fn\">r</span>)</span></span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">e</span> : <span class=\"fn\">R</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">hunit</span> : <span class=\"fn\">∀ (<span class=\"fn\">a</span> : <span class=\"fn\">α</span>), <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">op</span> <span class=\"fn\">e</span> <span class=\"fn\">a</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\">a</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">k</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">β</span> → <span class=\"fn\">α</span>)</span> → <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">Q</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">β</span> → <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Internal/Order/Basic.html#Lean.Order.PartialOrder.rel\">PartialOrder.rel</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Std/Internal/Do/Order/PreservesSup.html#Lean.Order.PreservesSup.frameClosure\">frameClosure</a> <span class=\"fn\">op</span> <span class=\"fn\">k</span> <span class=\"fn\">Q</span>)</span> <span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">k</span> <span class=\"fn\">Q</span>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The frame closure lies below the base transformer, witnessed at a unit resource `e` with\n`op e = id`. ","docLink":"./Std/Internal/Do/Order/PreservesSup.html#Lean.Order.PreservesSup.frameClosure_le","kind":"theorem","line":125,"name":"Lean.Order.PreservesSup.frameClosure_le","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Std/Internal/Do/Order/PreservesSup.lean#L125-L133"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Std/Internal/Do/Order/PreservesSup.html#Lean.Order.PreservesSup.upperAdjoint_mono\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Order</span>.<span class=\"name\">PreservesSup</span>.<span class=\"name\">upperAdjoint_mono</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Internal/Order/Basic.html#Lean.Order.CompleteLattice\">CompleteLattice</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">f</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span> → <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Std/Internal/Do/Order/PreservesSup.html#Lean.Order.PreservesSup\">PreservesSup</a> <span class=\"fn\">f</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">b </span><span class=\"fn\">b'</span> : <span class=\"fn\">α</span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">h</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Internal/Order/Basic.html#Lean.Order.PartialOrder.rel\">PartialOrder.rel</a> <span class=\"fn\">b</span> <span class=\"fn\">b'</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Internal/Order/Basic.html#Lean.Order.PartialOrder.rel\">PartialOrder.rel</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Std/Internal/Do/Order/PreservesSup.html#Lean.Order.PreservesSup.upperAdjoint\">upperAdjoint</a> <span class=\"fn\">f</span> <span class=\"fn\">b</span>)</span> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Std/Internal/Do/Order/PreservesSup.html#Lean.Order.PreservesSup.upperAdjoint\">upperAdjoint</a> <span class=\"fn\">f</span> <span class=\"fn\">b'</span>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"A right adjoint is monotone. ","docLink":"./Std/Internal/Do/Order/PreservesSup.html#Lean.Order.PreservesSup.upperAdjoint_mono","kind":"theorem","line":120,"name":"Lean.Order.PreservesSup.upperAdjoint_mono","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Std/Internal/Do/Order/PreservesSup.lean#L120-L123"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Std/Internal/Do/Order/PreservesSup.html#Lean.Order.PreservesSup.le_frameClosure\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Order</span>.<span class=\"name\">PreservesSup</span>.<span class=\"name\">le_frameClosure</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Int