s=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Internal/Order/Basic.html#Lean.Order.PartialOrder.rel\">PartialOrder.rel</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">op</span> <span class=\"fn\">r</span> <span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">k</span> <span class=\"fn\">Q'</span>)</span>)</span> <span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">k</span> <span class=\"fn\">fun (<span class=\"fn\">a</span> : <span class=\"fn\">β</span>) =&gt; <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">op</span> <span class=\"fn\">r</span> <span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">Q'</span> <span class=\"fn\">a</span>)</span></span></span>)</span></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">hpre</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Internal/Order/Basic.html#Lean.Order.PartialOrder.rel\">PartialOrder.rel</a> <span class=\"fn\">pre</span> <span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">k</span> <span class=\"fn\">Q</span>)</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Internal/Order/Basic.html#Lean.Order.PartialOrder.rel\">PartialOrder.rel</a> <span class=\"fn\">pre</span> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Std/Internal/Do/Order/PreservesSup.html#Lean.Order.PreservesSup.frameClosure\">frameClosure</a> <span class=\"fn\">op</span> <span class=\"fn\">k</span> <span class=\"fn\">Q</span>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Landing below the frame closure reduces to landing below the base transformer together with\nframing: if `pre ⊑ k Q` and `k` frames every `op r` (`op r (k Q') ⊑ k (fun a => op r (Q' a))`), then\n`pre ⊑ frameClosure op k Q`. ","docLink":"./Std/Internal/Do/Order/PreservesSup.html#Lean.Order.PreservesSup.le_frameClosure","kind":"theorem","line":109,"name":"Lean.Order.PreservesSup.le_frameClosure","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Std/Internal/Do/Order/PreservesSup.lean#L109-L118"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"