pan class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The upper adjoint of `f`: the join of all `x` with `f x ⊑ b`. For `f = (a ⊓ ·)` this is Heyting\nimplication `a ⇨ ·`. ","docLink":"./Std/Internal/Do/Order/PreservesSup.html#Lean.Order.PreservesSup.upperAdjoint","kind":"def","line":35,"name":"Lean.Order.PreservesSup.upperAdjoint","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Std/Internal/Do/Order/PreservesSup.lean#L35-L37"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Std/Internal/Do/Order/PreservesSup.html#Lean.Order.PreservesSup.map_sup\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Order</span>.<span class=\"name\">PreservesSup</span>.<span class=\"name\">map_sup</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">inst✝</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Internal/Order/Basic.html#Lean.Order.CompleteLattice\">CompleteLattice</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">f</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span> → <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Std/Internal/Do/Order/PreservesSup.html#Lean.Order.PreservesSup\">PreservesSup</a> <span class=\"fn\">f</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span> → <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Prop</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">f</span> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Internal/Order/Basic.html#Lean.Order.CompleteLattice.sup\">CompleteLattice.sup</a> <span class=\"fn\">s</span>)</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Internal/Order/Basic.html#Lean.Order.CompleteLattice.sup\">CompleteLattice.sup</a> <span class=\"fn\">fun (<span class=\"fn\">y</span> : <span class=\"fn\">α</span>) =&gt; <a href=\"./Init/Core.html#Exists\">∃</a> <a href=\"./Init/Core.html#Exists\">(</a><span class=\"fn\">x</span> <a href=\"./Init/Core.html#Exists\">:</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span><a href=\"./Init/Core.html#Exists\">)</a><a href=\"./Init/Core.html#Exists\">,</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">s</span> <span class=\"fn\">x</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#And\">∧</a> <span class=\"fn\">y</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">f</span> <span class=\"fn\">x</span></span></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"`f` preserves joins. ","docLink":"./Std/Internal/Do/Order/PreservesSup.html#Lean.Order.PreservesSup.map_sup","kind":"theorem","line":30,"name":"Lean.Order.PreservesSup.map_sup","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Std/Internal/Do/Order/PreservesSup.lean#L30-L30"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Std/Internal/Do/Order/PreservesSup.html#Lean.Order.PreservesSup.mk\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Order</span>.<span class=\"name\">PreservesSup</span>.<span class=\"name\">mk</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\">∀ {<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u} [<span class=\"fn\">inst</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Internal/Order/Basic.html#Lean.Order.CompleteLattice\">Lean.Order.CompleteLattice</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>] {<span class=\"fn\">f</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span> → <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>},\n  <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">(∀ (<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span> → <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Prop</a></span>),\n      <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">f</span> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Internal/Order/Basic.html#Lean.Order.CompleteLattice.sup\">Lean.Order.CompleteLattice.sup</a> <span class=\"fn\">s</span>)</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Internal/Order/Basic.html#Lean.Order.CompleteLattice.sup\">Lean.Order.CompleteLattice.sup</a> <span class=\"fn\">fun (<span class=\"fn\">y</span> : <span class=\"fn\">α</span>) =&gt; <a href=\"./Init/Core.html#Exists\">∃</a> <a href=\"./Init/Core.html#Exists\">(</a><span class=\"fn\">x</span> <a href=\"./Init/Core.html#Exists\">:</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span><a href=\"./Init/Core.html#Exists\">)</a><a href=\"./Init/Core.html#Exists\">,</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">s</span> <span class=\"fn\">x</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#And\">∧</a> <span class=\"fn\">y</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">f</span> <span class=\"fn\">x</span></span></span></span>)</span> →\n    <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Std/Internal/Do/Order/PreservesSup.html#Lean.Order.PreservesSup\">Lean.Order.PreservesSup</a> <span class=\"fn\">f</span></span></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Std/Internal/Do/Order/PreservesSup.html#Lean.Order.PreservesSup.mk","kind":"ctor","line":19,"name":"Lean.Order.PreservesSup.mk","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Std/Internal/Do/Order/PreservesSup.lean#L19-L31"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">class</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Std/Internal/Do/Order/PreservesSup.html#Lean.Order.PreservesSup\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Order</span>.<span class=\"name\">PreservesSup</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Internal/Order/Basic.html#Lean.Order.CompleteLattice\">CompleteLattice</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">f</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span> → <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Prop</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"`f : α → α` *preserves `Sup`* if it distributes over arbitrary joins:\n`f (sup s) = sup { f x | x ∈ s }`. Equivalently `f` is a lower adjoint, so it has an upper adjoint\n`PreservesSup.upperAdjoint f`.\n\nA frame operator acts by a `Sup`-preserving map for each resource `r`: the lattice meet `(a ⊓ ·)`,\nor a cost combinator `(costConj r)` for a counter resource. The upper adjoint is the corresponding\nimplication: Heyting `⇨` for the meet, a magic wand for separating conjunction.\n","docLink":"./Std/Internal/Do/Order/PreservesSup.html#Lean.Order.PreservesSup","kind":"class","line":19,"name":"Lean.Order.PreservesSup","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Std/Internal/Do/Order/PreservesSup.lean#L19-L31"}}],"imports":["Std.Internal.Do.Order.Basic"],"instances":[],"name":"Std.Internal.Do.Order.PreservesSup"}